


   OCaml-FPDF is an OCaml translation of the FPDF library (www.fpdf.org),
   with additions.


COPYRIGHT:

  This software is distributed under the GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE
  Version 2.1. See the enclosed file LICENSE for more details.


DEPENDENCIES:

  * OCaml 4.00.0;
  * Xml-light;
  * LablGtk2 (optional, for the markup editor widget).


INSTALL:

  Change to the ocamlfpdf toplevel directory and execute:

    ocaml _build.ml build fpdf
    ocaml _build.ml build test && pushd src/tests && ./test.opt && popd

  Install (as root) with:

    ocaml _build.ml install fpdf

  By default, the library will be installed in the `ocamlc -where`/fpdf
  directory.

  You can generate a LablGtk2 markup editor (for use with PDFMarkup) with:

    ocaml _build.ml build markup-editor
    ocaml _build.ml build markup-editor && src/tests/test_pdfmarkup_editor.opt
    ocaml _build.ml install markup-editor

HOW TO USE:

  Compile your program as follows:

  ocamlc -o ??? -I +fpdf -I +xml-light str.cma unix.cma xml-light.cma fpdf.cma ???.ml


